snippet.title: COLD ABYSS Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
COLD ABYSS is a relaxing and atmospheric exploration game where you repair internet cables on the bottom of the ocean.

There are no enemies or other forms of danger down there. Just you.

The perfect game to unwind after a long day.

Download for free here: https://studio-notes.itch.io/cold-abyss
